# Whitelist model: ignore everything in the repo root, then re-include only what belongs.
# This keeps all local-only material (docs, decompiled source, graphics, logs, IDE and tool
# folders) out of the repo without having to name each one.
/*

# Re-include the project itself:
!/.gitignore
!/TINB.ArticulatedBuses.sln
!/TINB.ArticulatedBuses/
!/TINB.ArticulatedBuses.Tests/

# Build output, caches and IDE user files inside the projects:
bin/
obj/
Library/
*.user
*.suo
